Global Surgical Video Recorder Market Insights
Surgical Video Recorder Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Surgical Video Recorder Market Overview
The global Surgical Video Recorder Market was valued at approximately USD 350 million in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.5% over the forecast period from 2024 to 2030. The demand for advanced surgical video recording systems has been increasing rapidly due to the growing adoption of minimally invasive surgeries, increasing need for high-quality documentation, and rising investments in healthcare infrastructure. Surgeons and medical professionals are increasingly relying on these systems for better patient outcomes, education, and surgical training. Key players are innovating in the space to offer highly specialized features and improved video quality for enhanced surgical experiences.

